title: Falafel Bejrut - Nowolipki
typeOfFood: Vegan, Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Lebanese
description: Lebanese eatery offering falafel-based meals and has hummus, tabouleh, dish of the day, makdus, maghmour, baklava and beverages including house-made lemonade. Owner is from Beirut. Has vegan cheese. This is its 2nd outlet in the city and is reported to have become all-vegan as of Mar 2016.
